{
  "id": "5de31569ca4f1700176ca068",
  "title": "同時に撮影しても映るものが違う",
  "created": 1575163259,
  "updated": 1575168384,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5de31569ca4f1700176ca068",
      "text": "同時に撮影しても映るものが違う",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575163259,
      "updated": 1575163836
    },
    {
      "id": "5de317a9aff09e00007ec103",
      "text": "iPhone7とiPhone11で同時に撮影をしても映るものには0.3秒程度の差がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575163818,
      "updated": 1575163852
    },
    {
      "id": "5de3157baff09e00007ec0ff",
      "text": "\t[https://gyazo.com/649afd66e5e2b0ecd249082f8ed15719]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575163259,
      "updated": 1575163853
    },
    {
      "id": "5de316dcaff09e0000d2250a",
      "text": "\t[https://gyazo.com/052562f18bea360264129fd57359265e]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575163806,
      "updated": 1575163855
    },
    {
      "id": "5de3165daff09e0000d22506",
      "text": "\t[https://gyazo.com/13181e6f1de8c8c30e7451938d5623d9]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575163485,
      "updated": 1575163861
    },
    {
      "id": "5de3169caff09e0000d22509",
      "text": "\t[https://gyazo.com/3a658382cfbc96594b4bc645efdfa2a0]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575163548,
      "updated": 1575163928
    },
    {
      "id": "5de31c47aff09e00007ec104",
      "text": "\t同時に撮ったのにiPhone7は50.58, iPhone11は50.27が映っている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575165000,
      "updated": 1575165024
    },
    {
      "id": "5de31812aff09e0000d2250c",
      "text": "\t動画 [Facebook https://www.facebook.com/nishiohirokazu/posts/10219958038997866?comment_id=10219958052198196&reply_comment_id=10219961618567353]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575163922,
      "updated": 1575164946
    },
    {
      "id": "5de31783aff09e00007ec100",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575163779,
      "updated": 1575163779
    },
    {
      "id": "5de320bbaff09e0000092a42",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/17972286727b3032c7008337822ff9db]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575166143,
      "updated": 1575166143
    },
    {
      "id": "5de321f0aff09e00007ec109",
      "text": "観測事実まとめ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575166449,
      "updated": 1575166455
    },
    {
      "id": "5de320beaff09e0000092a43",
      "text": "\tiPhone7もiPhone11も普段0.14秒程度現実から遅れたものがディスプレイに映っている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575166143,
      "updated": 1575166234
    },
    {
      "id": "5de3211aaff09e00007ec106",
      "text": "\t\tiPhone11だけ、シャッターを押した後からさらに遅れ始める",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575166234,
      "updated": 1575166586
    },
    {
      "id": "5de31bb2aff09e0000092a40",
      "text": "\t\tその遅れは後でジャンプして取り戻している",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575164851,
      "updated": 1575166573
    },
    {
      "id": "5de32251aff09e00007ec10a",
      "text": "\t撮影された写真は",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575166546,
      "updated": 1575166595
    },
    {
      "id": "5de32294aff09e00007ec10c",
      "text": "\t\tiPhone7では暗転しているあたりの時刻",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575166613,
      "updated": 1575166709
    },
    {
      "id": "5de322f4aff09e00007ec10e",
      "text": "\t\tiPhone11ではシャッターを押したあたりの時刻",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575166709,
      "updated": 1575166715
    },
    {
      "id": "5de322faaff09e00007ec10f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575166715,
      "updated": 1575166715
    },
    {
      "id": "5de3230caff09e00007ec110",
      "text": "解釈",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575166733,
      "updated": 1575166737
    },
    {
      "id": "5de32311aff09e00007ec112",
      "text": "\tもともとiPhone7では暗転のタイミングで撮影されていた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575166737,
      "updated": 1575166952
    },
    {
      "id": "5de323e7aff09e00007ec113",
      "text": "\t\t暗転が",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575166952,
      "updated": 1575167092
    },
    {
      "id": "5de32473aff09e00007ec116",
      "text": "\t\t\t「画面描画に使う計算リソースを別の用途に使うために必要」だったのか、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575167092,
      "updated": 1575167092
    },
    {
      "id": "5de32424aff09e00007ec114",
      "text": "\t\t\tそれとも鏡で目と撮像素子を切り替えるタイプの一眼レフの挙動を真似たのか、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575167013,
      "updated": 1575167093
    },
    {
      "id": "5de3230daff09e00007ec111",
      "text": "\t\tはわからない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575166733,
      "updated": 1575167096
    },
    {
      "id": "5de32478aff09e00007ec118",
      "text": "\tしかしこの挙動は「画面を見てベストタイミングでシャッターを押してもその0.3秒後が映る」ということでもあった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575167096,
      "updated": 1575167265
    },
    {
      "id": "5de32476aff09e00007ec117",
      "text": "\t\tこのズレが好ましくないことだという議論があったのだろう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575167095,
      "updated": 1575167312
    },
    {
      "id": "5de3254daff09e00007ec11a",
      "text": "\tiPhone11ではシャッターが押されたタイミングでの写真が撮られるようになった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575167309,
      "updated": 1575167375
    },
    {
      "id": "5de325f5aff09e00007ec11b",
      "text": "\t\tそのタイミングでディスプレイの内容を保存する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575167477,
      "updated": 1575167509
    },
    {
      "id": "5de32615aff09e00007ec11d",
      "text": "\t\t\t「このタイミングで撮像素子の内容を保存する」ではない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575167509,
      "updated": 1575167677
    },
    {
      "id": "5de326bcaff09e00007ec11e",
      "text": "\t\t\tディスプレイを見ないで撮影する人からすると、押したタイミングより0.13秒手前が映る",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575167677,
      "updated": 1575167700
    },
    {
      "id": "5de32810aff09e00009465c2",
      "text": "\t\t\t大部分のユーザはディスプレイを見て撮影するのでそちらに合わせたのだろう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575168016,
      "updated": 1575168046
    },
    {
      "id": "5de3290eaff09e00009465c3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575168271,
      "updated": 1575168271
    },
    {
      "id": "5de3290eaff09e00009465c5",
      "text": "関連",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575168271,
      "updated": 1575168343
    },
    {
      "id": "5de32957aff09e00009465c8",
      "text": "\t[現実よりも一拍遅くシャッターを切る]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575168343,
      "updated": 1575168344
    },
    {
      "id": "5de32958aff09e00009465c9",
      "text": "\t\tこちらの実験は人間がものを見てからシャッターを押すまでの反射神経の影響がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575168344,
      "updated": 1575168370
    },
    {
      "id": "5de32973aff09e00009465ca",
      "text": "\t\tその影響を排除しようとしてこの実験をした",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575168371,
      "updated": 1575168384
    },
    {
      "id": "5de32957aff09e00009465c7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575168343,
      "updated": 1575168343
    }
  ]
}